content: I really like this game, so I bought the full game. I ran into an issue with one of the game puzzles. The patches where the player has to restore the carpet design. I've solved this puzzle numerous times, but I am unable to get the puzzle piece. I uninstalled it restalled it, I've rebooted my phone. I know it's not an operator error. Perhaps the is a bug to be fixed.
Fun and inexpensive, the best combo!

Very disappointed that I cannot play w other profiles. This is the main reason for only 3 stars. Other than that, I like it. Developed a glitch in the bonus game that I could not retrieve the flower paint chip from the tapestry in the cabin. It thinks I still need to stitch the patches in place to retrieve the paint chip. I just deleted the game. No point in re-downloading it as I can't change the profile - so the issue will still be there. 2 stars...
Good addition to the series. This is probably the best developer in this genre. Always look forward to new titles in any of their franchises.

I love this game maker! Have played everything. Totally worth the price, always. This one felt maybe a little shorter and the controls seemed a bit more challenging. I will still be waiting for the next 5bn game and I'm recommending to anyone who enjoys this storyline, try the others as well!!! Best puzzle games.
These types of mystery, find objects and solving puzzle adventures are so captivating.
Lush and detailed artwork and realistic animation. Good storyline. I wish the main game was longer but we are grateful to get anything for android!. Another great game from 5BN.
